  "description": "<i>The Black Tower</i> is an illustrated or graphical fantasy text adventure.<br><br>There are many legends in this land but one stands above all, the legend of The Morjan Crystal. It is said by some that the crystal is the source of all evil and that when it is gone the land will be great once more. Others say the crystal protects the land and that without it all would wither and die. It is your task to travel to the Black Tower, solve puzzles, battle strange creatures and destroy the crystal.<br><br>This game is in two parts, &amp; to complete part two the player will need a code word that is provided at the end of part one.\n",
